  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, randomized study of total hip arthroplasty with and without the use of
      Radlink surgical positioning software. The investigators are interested in discovering
      whether the use of the Radlink software will provide more accurate acetabular cup position
      when compared with surgeon estimates based on visual inspection of fluoroscopic images.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
